== Russian ==

=== Etymology ===
'''фарт''' &larr; Russian fenya ''фарт'' &larr; {{italbrac|possibly}} German [[Fahrt]] ([[ride]]) &larr; German [[fahren]] (to [[drive]], [[везти]]) because of [[везти]] means ''to drive'' and ''to have luck'' in Russian; or ''possibly'' from [[фортуна]] ([[fortune]]) meaning a [[luck]]

=== Noun ===
[[Category:Russian nouns]]
'''фарт''' (fart) {{m}} {{italbrac|singular only|informal}}

# [[luck]], [[fortune]]
# [[destiny]]

